longBusinessSummary: FOMO Corp. focuses on sale of disinfection products and personal protective equipment. It is also involved in the LED lighting business. The company was formerly known as 2050 Motors, Inc. and changed its name to FOMO Corp. in December 2019. FOMO Corp. is based in Chicago, Illinois.
